usses its meaning for a current, »modernized« art history.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aDorner. 4aKant. 4aKunst. 4aKunstgeschichte. 4aKunsttheorie. 4aKunstwissenschaft. 4aPanofsky. 4aPostmoderne. 4aRaum. 4aÄsthetik. 7aART / History / General.2bisacsh  aAesthetics.  aArt History.  aArt.  aFine Arts.  aPostmodernism.  aSpace.  aTheory of Art.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2015z9783110438642oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839427156zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839427156423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839427156/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKAb2015  aZDB-23-TGPb2014  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016